This sample application supplements the `Getting Started with Grails` 
presentation.  

http://www.nofluffjuststuff.com/show_session_view.jsp?presentationId=8669&showId=104

-This application uses the built-in in-memory HSQLDB that comes with every
Grails app.

-You may need to execute `grails upgrade` prior to running the app.

-After executing `grails run-app` to start the application, navigate to
http://localhost:8080/racetrack.